WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.266 --> 00:00:04.033
Sure enough, the water came as I thought

2
00:00:05.366 --> 00:00:07.366
How about Xia Ruyan?

3
00:00:07.666 --> 00:00:09.800
You ran away with my daughter for five years

4
00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:12.466
Should this account be carefully calculated?

5
00:00:12.566 --> 00:00:13.733
You got it?

6
00:00:13.733 --> 00:00:15.700
The woman from five years ago was you

7
00:00:15.700 --> 00:00:16.733
Still want to lie to me

8
00:00:16.733 --> 00:00:18.366
Since Sisi is my child

9
00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:19.666
Should go back to the Lu family

10
00:00:19.700 --> 00:00:21.100
Sissy is your daughter, that's right

11
00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:22.866
But he's been with me since I was a kid

12
00:00:22.866 --> 00:00:24.033
He has a simple personality.

13
00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:26.300
It is not suitable for the complex environment of your Lu family at all.

14
00:00:26.533 --> 00:00:27.500
As for Xiaoji

15
00:00:27.566 --> 00:00:29.666
I believe that in your capacity

16
00:00:29.666 --> 00:00:31.866
There must also be many women willing to have children with you

17
00:00:31.866 --> 00:00:33.466
Not three years from now.

18
00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:35.266
I'll take Xiaoji with me today

19
00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:36.533
Listen to you

20
00:00:36.533 --> 00:00:38.333
Is to grab custody of the child from me

21
00:00:38.333 --> 00:00:39.700
Make sure you can rob me

22
00:00:39.733 --> 00:00:41.100
I am the mother of the child

23
00:00:41.100 --> 00:00:42.200
Although the law requires

24
00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:44.133
Children should try to follow their mother until the age of 10

25
00:00:44.133 --> 00:00:45.266
But only if

26
00:00:45.366 --> 00:00:47.000
The mother's economic strength has to keep up

27
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:48.366
I will definitely work hard to make money.

28
00:00:48.366 --> 00:00:50.000
Provide her with the highest quality educational environment

29
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:51.066
That was before

30
00:00:51.400 --> 00:00:54.000
Now you think I'll give you another chance?

31
00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:55.433
You threaten me?

